# Pin the public registry for THIS project so package-lock.json always records
# registry.npmjs.org URLs. The dev box's global .npmrc points at a Tencent
# Cloud internal mirror; lockfiles generated against it are uninstallable on
# GitHub Actions runners (the mirror is unreachable from the public internet),
# which broke CI once already. Project config overrides the global one.
registry=https://registry.npmjs.org/
